Like I said before, getting a swarm was a rarity. I could pull a single, say, Curmudgeon out of a group of 4 without any but the one I attack coming at me. It's only if I stay within aggro range for the time it takes for them to aggro that I get more. And, it's been proven countless times that a puller for a group will almost always bring back more then one. Denying this not only completely contradicts <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> what the developers said</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, but displays a lack of knowledge of the game itself.<br>
