<br>
However, the game does have BAF coding (bring a friend) meaning more mobs will come from a camp in direct purportion to the number of people you have in your group.<br>
<br>
However...it can be buggy. For example if another group hits your mob, or aids you in any way, or you them <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>during</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> a fight...your next pull will likely BAF. The coding sees you as part of the group. This was to probably to prevent people from getting mass exp by single pulling purples to a large group. Or could just be buggy, dunno. <br>
<br>
But yah, most of the time you don't get adds when you solo. <p><a href="http://www.anarchyboard.com" target="_blank">
